Name: UHUD CRAFTS Beautiful Antique Wooden Fold-able Side Table/End Table/Plant Stand/Stool Living Room Kids Play Furniture Table Round Shape
Review: I wanted two loungers to be placed under my trees in my garden. Since this lounger was priced almost half (or more) of some of the better known brands, I was a tad worried about ordering this. So, I first ordered one to see how well made it is. I was quite impressed with the fit and finish of the product and it was ergonomically perfect to lounge. Having seen how good the lounger was, I order another one and now I have two. Since the loungers are placed under the trees and away from direct sun, I feel it will age very well. The way I see it, if it lasts for 4 or 5 years, it is paisa vasool. :) One small complaint I had was that the bolts holding the thing together should have been made from rust-resistant material or at least painted. The cushion is made of rexine sort of material. I fully expect the cats to tear it up in no time. Probably, a treated fabric sort of material would have been better but I guess the price would have gone up quite a bit if that is the case. Anyway, overall I am super satisifed. Attaching some photos.
